<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
HiLoOpenClose Chart Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
HiLoOpenClose Chart is a special kind of chart that is normally used in stock analysis. This chart type expects 4 Y values for every point in the series. Those values should represent the High, Low, Open and Close values of the stock, in that order, for that period.
</Paragraph>


